column5: You may have taught the family a few things in life TJ, but fishing ain't one of them. Nicely done Jaden.

Had a quick weekend at Jiggy, the fish were on.  Jaden got a beautiful bass off the dock on a hammerhead topwater.      Even the weather cooperated with us for the most part... didn't see any partridges though.. need more leaves to be gone I think!!
The girls in this family "ROCK"
ummm nice Bass?
Doesn't TJ get cold swimming under the dock to hook those on for you girls?  JF

That's a beaut alright  That kid knows more than I do cause I was lookin for big smallies down deep this past weekend and struck out with turnover going on.  I should have been tossin docks I reckon.  Good stuff  Bushart
I love the coloration on that bass. Something kinda cool about the camo look in Fall LOL!
nice fish
The videos...
Nice pics, you have taugh her well...lol
Great report, pics and videos TJ Loved the release!!!  Congrats to Jaden on that monster bronzeback Leechman
You must get huge feelings of inadequacy boss! I mean more than the usual...........
Truer words were never spoken.
That's some bass.......
LOL John  Did you happen to notice the depth at the dock? Dought he gets under there.  Thats a great catch there Jaden.
Nice fish Jaden,you will always out fish the PINK tutu man LOL.  Steve
That`s fantastic, Jaden! Way to go, you`ve gotten to be quite the fisherlady!
Nice bronzeback for sure. Must have gave her a nice fight.
oh snap it's the lock ness monster
great pics....
Good fish!  on topwter to boot.  nice
You got that right!!!   I dunno which one is cuter, Jayden or the Bass!!!  ... and Momma holding the Pike is awesome as well!!!
thats just awesome BOSS congrats Jaden very nice bass
Awesome job Jaden...Beauty bass for sure.  You rock!  Great pike Monique
You taught her well old man, looks like she may of beat out my PB smallie this year(3lb 4oz)  Great job!!  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
Nice Jaden & Momma Nice Pictures & Nicer Video
